nodes.text: During the First Order/Resistance War, shortly after the Battle of Crait, General Leia Organa assigned Wedge Antilles and his team, dubbed Corellian Team Two, on a mission to Coronet City on Corellia, to rescue political prisoners being held in secret by the First Order. Among the prisoners included a former New Republic Senator Ransolm Casterfo, a long time friend to Organa, whom she thought was killed many years ago.
